###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_06105004
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_06105004> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                               rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000016> ;
                                               <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A disposition which inheres in materials capable of becoming rigid when cured by heating."@en ;
                                               <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/contributor> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2996-719X> ,
                                                                                             <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1072-8081> ;
